<p dir="auto">Hey , I am Siavash Gorji, born on 1991/06/25 in Tehran, I graduated from Basu.ac.ir University in the field of Fluid Mechanics Engineering in 2014 and also graduated from Islamic Azad University in the field of Computer Engineering, Software Branch in 2023. In 2018, I started learning and working in the web2 field at Atlas Web site design company(gowebsite.ir), and at first I worked as a frontend developer and later as a backend developer, then I started my own site and company called teksite(teksite.net), which is a dedicated site. whose backend is implemented with the laravel framework and also the portfolios (websites) that I have designed are displayed.Also, due to my great interest in artificial intelligence, I decided to continue my studies in the field of artificial intelligence at the Islamic Revolution University in master level(cuir.ac.ir), and I am currently studying in this university.
